```json
    point = {
        "id": article['article_id'],
        "payload": {
            "page_content": page_content,
            "metadata": {
                "article": article,
                "type": article["meta_type"],
                "timestamp": int(datetime.strptime(article["pubDate"], '%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%S%z').timestamp()),
                "add_date": int(datetime.now(timezone.utc).timestamp())
            }
        }
    }
```

I've created a payload index on a collection using the API, when I check the info on the collection, I see:

```json
    "payload_schema": {
